n, Accent Flavor Enhancer enhances food flavor naturally.'),(1072,'B0028OSX78','Product Description','Oxydol Powdered Cp U2 31 Use - 4 Pack'),(1083,'B004MDNGU2','Product Description','The TT-1L Lithium battery powered flashlight features dual lighting modes and the latest in LED technology. The C4 power LED with its textured reflector provides an even beam, along with a piercing hotspot for distance. The three ultra bright LEDs provide area lighting and extended run time. Packaged with a high-strength lanyard. Machined aluminum case with non-slip knurled grip and a matte black anodized finish. Unbreakable polycarbonate lens. Light source is three (3) ultra bright white LEDs with 100,000 hour lifetime. Flashlight features C4 LED technology, impervious to shock with a 50,000 hour lifetime. IPX4 rated for water resistant operation. All openings O-ring sealed. 1 meter impact resistance tested.'),(1084,'B0006NFDQ2','Product Description','Norton Consumer 85440 Crystolon Bench Combination Sharpening Stones Norton Consumer 85440 Crystolon Bench Combination Sharpening Stones Features: ; Oil-filled; Fast cutting action; Combination grits, fine on one side and coarse on other side; Carded; 85440: 4\"; 85445: 5\"; 87935: 6\"; 85455: 8\"'),(1089,'B007D9JVOM','Product Description','Focus on high quality and classic elegant design, These fashion jewelry pieces easily go with any style like round collar, V-neck or the back collar. Three Crystal Square  Gold tone highlights your taste and unique individuality and the subtle simple elegant design can be worn on to almost any occasion.'),(1094,'B00189146Q','Product Description','These cufflinks are great for everyday wear, special occasions and weddings. They make a perfect gift for the Groom and Groomsmen, that special someone, or just for yourself!   Enamel & Silver Plated. Display Beautifully in Included Jewelry Box.  Bullet Back Closure.  Dimensions: Approx. 3/4\" Diameter'),(1114,'B005E9W9S8','Product Description','U2 Steel Fridge Magnet'),(1124,'B0050B2X0Y','Product Description','Four 4-foot by 4-foot by 34-inch High PVC Greenhouses on a 4-foot by 12-foot by 12-foot by 12-inch - \"U -shaped\" Raised Garden Base in Western Red Cedar - homegrown in the Pacific North West - is assembled with select high quality Cedar timbers. Red Cedar is naturally insect and rot resistant. Patented Frame-It-All stacking joints plus the new 4 way joint ensure the raised bed shape is 100-percent true. The greenhouse frames snap together effortlessly and each corner locates into the top of the corner joint. Carefully place the PVC greenhouse cover over the frames and secure each corner to the Frame-It-All raised garden bed with the string tabs. Both side windows open up for complete access and have stays to hold them open at your desired height for free air flow. Erect the greenhouses at the first hint of spring to seed early and provide protection. Extend the growing season as well by using the Greenhouses to extend the growing season into fall and winter. Raised Gardens are better than in-ground for growing at home because you can control the quality of the soil and nutrients. You will also get a larger crop to pick of veggies, fruits, and flowers. Raised beds are easy to manage with access from all sides, and because they are above the ground surface, they have better drainage. No clumpy, hard soil to turn, and almost no back breaking weeding to do. Raised Beds are quick and easy to assemble with little effort.'),(1133,'B002SSNFFY','Product Description','The Lockheed U-2, nicknamed \"Dragon Lady\", is a single-engine, very high-altitude reconnaissance aircraft operated by the United States Air Force and previously flown by the Central Intelligence Agency. It provides day and night, very high-altitude (70,000 feet / 21,000 meters), all-weather surveillance.\nThe aircraft is also used for electronic sensor research and development, \nsatellite calibration, and satellite data validation.'),(1153,'B000K67VOW','P