or my preparation of the V3 Foundation Exam. I passed and thought I had scored 100%. I felt well-prepared going in, and that confidence makes it much easier to take the exam.\" Vince Pulice, ITIL V3 - Principle System Engineer - SuperValue <br /><br />\"I fo'),(1823,'B006JJTA2U','Product Description','This pocket guide is a quick, portable reference tool designed for managers, to give an overall picture of the ITIL V3 upgrade. Covering not only the ITIL V3 Service Lifecycle approach, to provide even greater value, this handy new guide also describes the ITIL V3 functions and processes in a separate section as well. Endorsed by APMG - the official accreditor of OGC, it is always one of our bestsellers and the key content is great for ITIL exam preparation. The ITIL Service Lifecycle and the ITIL processes and functions are listed separately for a better practical approach.'),(1824,'B006JJTA2U','Product Description','This pocket guide is a quick, portable reference tool designed for managers, to give an overall picture of the ITIL V3 upgrade. Covering not only the ITIL V3 Service Lifecycle approach, to provide even greater value, this handy new guide also describes the ITIL V3 functions and processes in a separate section as well. Endorsed by APMG - the official accreditor of OGC, it is always one of our bestsellers and the key content is great for ITIL exam preparation. The ITIL Service Lifecycle and the ITIL processes and functions are listed separately for a better practical approach.'),(1825,'B00422LLOG','Product Description','Here is a book written for CIOs, CTOs, and executive managers who want to learn more about Service Operation, a core ITIL lifecycle phase. In today\'s business and economic climates, more and more CIOs and CTOs are being asked to establish quality controls throughout their organizations. And when it comes to IT operations (the management of data centers, infrastructures, and technical support teams) ITIL has become the de facto worldwide standard. And so, more and more CIOs and CTOs are implementing one or more components of ITIL. This book is written primarily for those executives who are charged with this new mission, specifically a mission that includes IT services and their operations. This audience can benefit from a book that presents a strategic picture of the scope and reach of the Service Operation slice of ITIL without delving too deeply into the nuances of tactical implementation details. With this book, executives should be able to position their teams for an effective Service Operation design and implementation effort. The author, James Persse, presents a fundamental look at Service Operation with a focus on design and implementation while avoiding jargon, and concentrating on the activities, assets, and artifacts that make for a successful program. Covers... - Service Desk - Incident Management - Problem Management - Event Management - Request Fulfillment - Access Management - Monitoring & Control - IT Operations Plus... - Complete Overview of ITIL V3 - Typical Assets and Artifacts for each Service Operation area - Tips and Techniques for Successful Implementation - Sample Key Performance Indicators and Critical Success Factors'),(1826,'B0073885CW','Product Description','Welcome to this eBook containing a list of 160 of the top and most used ITIL v3 Foundation exam questions. There are no trick questions in this paper and they have all been checked and confirmed as valid and correct by ITIL practitioners from the UK.'),(1827,'B004SH6XLG','Product Description','As a final exam preparation tool, <i>CCIE Security v3.0 Quick Reference</i> provides a concise review of all objectives on the CCIE Security written exam v3.0 (350-018). This eBook provides you with detailed, graphical-based information, highlighting only the key topics in cram-style format. <p style=\"margin:0px;\"></p> <p style=\"margin:0px;\">Â </p> <p style=\"margin:0px;\">With this document as your guide, you will review topics on security protocols, encryption, application protocols, security technologies, Cisco IOS security features, Cisco ASA, security management, wireless security, IPv6 security, security policies, network attack mitigation, and computer forensics . This fact-filled Quick Reference allows you to get all-important information at a glance, helping you to focus your study on areas of weakness and to enhance memory retention of essential exam concepts.</p>'),(1828,'B007PVBJ5C','Product Description','+ \"The truth sometimes hurts, but when it crosses the line to downright funny, that\'s when Randy Cassingham swings into action.\" --Boardwatch<br /><br />+ \"And now for something completely different.\" --CNN Morning News<br /><br />+ \"Best in Net Entertainment.\" --Internet World<br /><br />This is True is one of the first Internet-based features, created by Randy Cassingham as an e-mail newsletter in early 1994. True\'s mission is to provoke thought through social commentary. But if readers aren\'t entertained by the stories, they won\'t read very many. Thus its vehicle, weird-but-true news from legitimate news sources from around the world. The result spans the gamut of the crazy things we humans think we can get away with: this collection of jaw-dropping examples of the human thought process, and the realization that we can do better â€” a lot better!<br /><br />What sort of stories?<br /><br />+ Two robbers were in the process of their crime when one changed his mind and arrested the other.<br /><br />+ Pigeons in Britain are so lazy they\'ve learned how to get around the city on commuter trains.<br /><br />+ A man sued his doctor because he survived his cancer longer than the doctor predicted.<br /><br />The weird-but-true stories come from all over the world, each one punctuated by Randy\'s wild commentary â€” a tagline that is humorous, ironic, opinionated, or (with luck) some combination of the three. \"Truth is stranger than fiction,\" Randy likes to say, \"because fiction has to make sense.\"<br /><br />This is Volume 3 of the series, collecting the third year of stories and headlines from mid-1996 to mid-1997. The newsletter is still active, too: see www.ThisIsTrue.com for details.'),(1829,'B0080R4NPI','Product Description','Mandalas coloring for relaxing,fun,meditation.<br /> <br />Mandala images preview - http://www.amind.co.kr/bbs/board.php?bo_table=mandalashop&wr_id=4<br /><br />58 Mandalas'),(1833,'B001BDEE52','Product Description','6\" X 3/4\" X 1\" TYPE 1 AZ80-K8-V3 GRINDING WHEEL'),(1834,'B003Y2MI8I','Product Description','BEARING-BALL #6001V3 For Kawasaki engine Replaces Part # 3115014211A'),(1835,'B002WTRXY8','Product Description','Brute Lawn Mower Parts # 44X6675MA DEC V3 DC 5X2 AUTO D'),(1836,'B000SATBQ6','Product Description','Tanaka Part CONTROLLER 805 DF166-H V3'),(1838,'B003Y2OWAA','Product Description','BEARING-BALL,6001V3 For Kawasaki engine Replaces Part # 92045-2060'),(1839,'B0083JG6ZS','Product Description','4X8 WZ2001T V3 Santa Rosa Plum Tree'),(1840,'B0018KJWSW','Product Description','Aqua Globes are an attractive solution for automatic houseplant watering. Fill he hand blown stained glass globes as the plant needs it. Aqua Globes are a great alternative to the daily chore of watering plants and an excellent choice for automatic watering while on vacation.  How Aqua Globes Work As soil becomes dry, it releases oxygen into the Aqua Globe, which in turn releases the exact amount of water your plant needs.  Automatically waters houseplants for up to 2 weeks. For indoor and outdoor potted plants. Hand-blown glass designs adds beauty to your plants. Includes gift boxes for sharing with friends & family Assorted Colors'),(1841,'B000070GUZ','Product Description','Snap away without worry.  More and more people trust Duracell Photo Batteries to give them the power they need to get those perfect pictures.'),(1842,'B000GA8QD2','Product Description','Replacement Digital Camera Battery NP-FR1 for Sony Cyber-shot