ce loaded, cell voltage drops to 3.0v.\n * Internal over-charge and over-discharge protection to prevent battery over use. The current will be shut off when the battery voltage drops below 2.5V.\n * Dimension: 16 D x 34 H mm. (The height 34mm includes the button top)\n * Weight: 17 g or 0.6 Oz.\n * Tenergy Li-Ion RCR123A 900mah batteries reach more than 3.0v at full charge. These cells should only be used in high quality CREE LED flashlights. Do not use in incandescent bulb flashlights!\n* NOT COMPATIBLE WITH SUREFIRE FLASHLIGHTS.'),(2685,'B001BLOQ2K','Product Description','* Rechargeable CR123A Li-Ion Batteries with 3.0V working voltage \n* Capacity: \n * Nominal: 600mAh\n * Maximum:900 mAh\n\n * Tenergy RCR123A can be recharged up to 1000 times. 1 RCR123A Li-ion = 1000 CR123A Primary Cells\n * Replace the most of CR123A primary Lithium battery for a digital cameras and flashlight. This battery is not compatible with SureFire Flashlights!\n\n * Internal voltage regulators.\n * Modified Voltage to achieve 3.2v at full voltage; once loaded, cell voltage drops to 3.0v.\n * Internal over-charge and over-discharge protection to prevent battery over use. The current will be shut off when the battery voltage drops below 2.5V.\n * Dimension: 16 D x 34 H mm. (The height 34mm includes the button top)\n * Weight: 17 g or 0.6 Oz.\n * This battery is not compatible with SureFire Flashlights!'),(2686,'B00186QNP6','Product Description','Tovatec Wide Angle Flashlight Torch with LED illumination. Modern LED technology means no costly bulbs to break or replace. With 100,000 hours of operational time, these LED-Feet s are good for a lifetime. Thoroughly tested, waterproof designs allow for use in nearly any environment.'),(2687,'B00186QNP6','Amazon.com','Designed for diving and other outdoor uses, this Intova Torch offers a wide angled 43-degree beam to cover more territory. The compact, yet powerful torch offers 220 lumens of bright light with a CREE LED that provides a usable lifespan of 100,000 hours. Waterproof to 400 feet and constructed with a double O-ring sealed anodized aluminum housing, the torch can be used on deep sea dives with confidence. A magnetic slide switch is designed for easy operation. The Wide Angle Torch carries a one year limited warranty from Intova and comes ready to use with batteries included.<p>  <table align=\"right\" cellpadding=\"10\" width=\"268\"> <tbody> <tr> <td><img align=\"top\" border=\"0\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://images.amazon.com/images/G/01/stores/sport-goods/detail-pages/B00186QNP6.jpg\" width=\"268 \" /><br /><br /><small><em><strong>The compact Intova torch provides a wide 43-degree beam angle.</strong></em></small></td> </tr> </tbody> </table>  <b>Features and Specifications:</b><ul> <li>Light Source: one CREE LED <li>LED lifetime: 100,000 hours <li>Lumens: 220 <li>Beam Angle: 43 degrees <li>Anodized aluminum housing <li>Magnetic slide switch <li>Waterproof to 400 feet (122 meters) <li>Double O-ring protection <li>Batteries: two CR123 batteries (included) <li>10 hour burn time <li>Dimensions: 5.8 by 1.4 inches (Length by Diameter) <li>Weight: 7.2 ounces (with batteries) <li>Color temp: 5000~6000K </ul><p>'),(2688,'B0023RSXSO','Product Description','The 220 Lumen LED Submersible Dive Light is the newest twist to the old flashlight. This 220 Lumen Dive Light is made of anodized aluminum construction, and is anti-corrosion proof via its hardened finish. The Dive Light contains a K2 Super Flux LED that offers state of the art performance. This flashlight provides 8 hours of continuous use on one set of alkaline batteries. The Dive Light is guaranteed to be submersible (IPX8) to a depth of up to 100 meters. On land, the center spot concentrates 80% of the light output while using the remaining 20% to provide a bright area around the center spot to light up a wide viewing area. Underwater more of the lights is concentrated into the beam providing superior performance. The flashlight comes complete with a nylon wrist lanyard.Product SpecificationsLumens: 220Run Time: 8 HoursBeam Distance: 200 FeetBulb Type: Cree Q4Batteries: 6 AAAProduct Material: Anodized AluminumProduct Dimensions:6.5\" L x 1.25\" WDimensions Head: 1.55\"Product Weight: .8 lbsAvailable Color(s): BlackSwitch: TwistAdditional Features: IPX8'),(2689,'B002KHDHU6','Product Description','Tovatec Compact Flashlight Torch with LED illumination. Modern LED technology means no costly bulbs to break or replace. With 100,000 hours of operational time, these LED-Feet s are good for a lifetime. Thoroughly tested, waterproof designs allow for use in nearly any environment.'),(2690,'B002KHDHU6','Amazon.com','<p>Ideal for using while snorkeling or diving as well as bringing along on camping and hiking trips, the Tovatec Compact Torch flashlight shines a bright 130 lumen light to guide you through the dark. Waterproof to 400 feet, the beam is focused for maximum distance and the switch provides settings for reduced beam and strobe features.</p> <h4>Specifications:</h4> <ul> <li>LED light: One 130-lumen CREE </li> <li>LED lifetime: 100,000 hours </li> <li>Depth rating: 400 feet (122 meters) </li> <li>Beam angle: 12 degrees </li> <li>Power: Three AAA (not included) </li> <li>Variable power: Yes -- full, 30 percent, and strobe </li> <li>Switch: Magnetic tail </li> <li>Burn time: Up to 6 hours (at full power) </li> <li>Dimensions: 5.5 inches long, 1.4-inch diameter </li> <li>Weight: 6.5 ounces (with batteries) </li> </ul>'),(2691,'B000R9D9S4','Product Description','Tovatec Aluminum Torch with LED illumination. Modern LED technology means no costly bulbs to break or replace. With 100,000 hours of operational time, these LED-Feet s are good for a lifetime. Thoroughly tested, waterproof designs allow for use in nearly any environment.'),(2692,'B000R9D9S4','Amazon.com','<p>Ideal for using while snorkeling or diving as well as bringing along on camping and hiking trips, the Tovatec Aluminum Torch flashlight (model IFL 660) shines an extra-bright 220 lumen light to guide you through the dark. Waterproof to 400 feet, the beam is focused for maximum distance and the switch provides settings for reduced beam and strobe features.</p> <h4>Specifications:</h4> <ul> <li>LED light: One 220-lumen CREE </li> <li>LED lifetime: 100,000 hours </li> <li>Depth rating: 400 feet (122 meters) </li> <li>Beam angle: 12 degrees </li> <li>Power: Two CR123 (included) </li> <li>Variable power: Yes -- full, 30 percent, and strobe </li> <li>Switch: Magnetic slide switch </li> <li>Burn time: Up to 10 hours (at full power) </li> <li>Dimensions: 6.2 inches long, 1.5-inch diameter </li> <li>Weight: 7.9 ounces (with batteries) </li> </ul>'),(2693,'B003UDY08M','Product Description','The <B>Intova Torch Handstrap</B> keeps your hands free when using your dive light. The soft velcro strap snugly wraps around your hand or wrist, and the durable nylon and neoprene sleeve securely attaches a variety of Intova underwater torches (IFL 600, Wide-Angle, Compact, Tactical, etc.) for hands-free lighting. Strap is adjustable, so one size fits all.'),(2695,'B001EZWMZQ','Product Description','Sennheiser OMX 95 VC Style II Headphones For those who appreciate both sound and style. The OMX 95 VC Style II are high-quality stereo earphones with an integrated volume control and adjustable ear clips for optimum fit and comfort. These deluxe clip-on earphones also feature a new damping system which produces a detailed sound pattern for a special listening pleasure while the smoothly brushed metal parts accentuate the earphones\' unique design and yield a luscious sheen. A carrying pouch for convenient handling and storage completes the package. Features Specially tuned damping system ensures detailed sound image and highest listening pleasure Smoothly brushed metal parts accentuate the unique design of the OMX 95-VC style II Adjustable ear clips ensure a custom secure fit Includes and ear adapter set to personlise the fit of the earbuds Volume control integrated in cable Carrying pouch included for convenient handling and storage Ideal for use with all MP3 iPod iPhone DVD/CD players and portable gaming systems Symmetrical cable 2-year warranty'),(2696,'B001XRR3YA','Product Description','Fluval Poly/Carbon Cartridges features two sides for effective chemical filtration, the crucial second stage in the filtration process. The polyester filter pad side filters out fine debris and contaminants. The carbon side filters out harmful liquid substances, colorants and odors. The Fluval Poly/Carbon Cartridge works in part with the Fluval Filter Foam Pad to help keep your aquarium healthy and clean.'),(2697,'B001XRXY1G','Product Description','Fluval U4 underwater Filter with three stage filtration is ideal for use in fresh, marine or reptile environments. Stage 1 foam removes large particles. In stage 2, the poly/carbon cartridge traps fine debris, improves water clarity and removes impurities. In stage 3, BioMax provides optimal biological filtration efficiency.'),(2698,'B001XRSSCQ','Product Description','The Fluval Foam Pad was designed specifically for the U2 filter model to captures large particles and debris for effective mechanical filtration, the crucial first stage in the filtration process. Custom fit to prevent bypass, they have a pore size that allows efficient water flow with less clogging for long-lasting filtration. The Fluval Foam Pad is for freshwater, marine or reptile environments.'),(2699,'B001XRR2IM','Product Description','Fluval BioMax provides an optimal environment for beneficial bacteria growth. The bio rings have a complex pore system creating an optimal environment where beneficial bacteria can thrive. It also reduces and controls ammonia and nitrate. Fluval BioMax is for freshwater and marine environments, and fits the U series filter models: U2,U3 and U4.'),(2700,'B0041ITM56','Product Description','These premium foam filter pads were custom designed and manufactured for the Fluval U2 Underwater filter.  As with all filter media, rinse the foam pad thoroughly before use.  Place the foam pad into the foam compartment of your U2 filter.  Rinse the foam pads alternately weekly and replace when the water circulation slows noticeably.  To ensure retention of the beneficial bacteria required for biological filtering, never change or rinse both pads at the same time.  Rinse with aquarium water, not tap water.'),(2701,'B002CZ0JUC','Product Description','Nutrafin Turtle Clean Biological Turtle Habitat Cleaner helps reduce maintenance by metabolizing waste in gravel, power filters, decorations and on interior turtle habitat surfaces. It rapidly reduces organic waste from feeding, turtle waste and expected skin and shell shedding as a result of growth. Nutrafin Turtle Clean Biological Turtle Habitat Cleaner also helps control odors while providing turtles with an improved aquatic habitat.'),(2702,'B001GAQ9YE','Product Description','Everlasting Treats are made from natural ingredients without plastics or polymers.  They are edible and digestible with an irresistible taste dogs love.  Raised dental ridges safely scrub the teeth clean.  Can be used as a snack anytime or inside the Everlasting Treat Ball for a chewing challenge.'),(2703,'B0088MMYWY','Product Description','<b>Notice: Please kindly contact us for the color you need after you purchase it within 8 hours. If not, we will ship a random color.</b><br>\nEight colors available: Black, Blue, Green, Hot Pink, Pink, Purple, White and Yellow.<br>\n1. 100% Brand New.<br>\n2. Waterproof and dustproof, protect your laptop against spills, dust,and other contaminants.<br>\n3. Removable and washable, the free cleaning without affecting the effectiveness of their use.<br>\n4. Material: High Quality Silicone.<br>\n5. Dimension: Due to your Laptop model.<br>\n6. Version: Apply to US Layout Keyboard.<br>\n7. <b>Special Notes: Our Protector is For US Type Keyboard ( NOT Europe Type) you can distinguish:</b><br>\n